{"tid":2157023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜求安慰","createTime":"2020-08-14T20:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T23:49:25.000Z","uid":302790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de8992fb7452c1dea8c358b3ce36e81d9d06aa4f","tid":2157023,"uid":302790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T20:48:10.000Z","msg":"所有野都係最近發生<br />\n同個傾左好耐計既朋友有啲呦叫<br />\n另一個識左好耐既好朋友有其他野做 <br />\n好似即刻忘記左自己咁<br />\n一直傾開計既人其實都久唔久覆一次<br />\n重點係以前都好似唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n聽聽下sad歌眼淚流左落泥<br />\n自己一直都比較樂觀 同自己講一個人都ok <br />\n唔想開黑post影響人心情 博關心<br />\n所以發現自己有唔開心都唔會有人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人未訓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2ea128b5e285684b46f81c17d738db94b2bcfb","tid":2157023,"uid":139027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:50:07.000Z","msg":"人生係咁㗎啦，有時你expect你喺佢哋心目中佔有重要地位，但到頭來你會發現其實冇想像中咁重要，或者只係普通朋友"},{"pid":"c63c0732884276a15b4588bc4d9e2e29bbffd849","tid":2157023,"uid":321400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b26dcc88efc74b1ad16d8eb3a4f0e8430b0c74","tid":2157023,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:55:04.000Z","msg":"溝仔"},{"pid":"ca6ca6f204820ffc62f7cbba8c46e2d331b19482","tid":2157023,"uid":297409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:49:25.000Z","msg":"從來都自己一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}